{"tid":653913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網購「志玲姐」撫失戀　買家開箱嚇到想收驚","createTime":"2018-05-05T07:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T09:06:16.000Z","uid":72009,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"321b1b0706e0ef387151cff95b1c01dd8570f929","tid":653913,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:10:31.000Z","msg":"「這是一個遇到網絡詐騙集團的心酸故事......。」台北市一名暱稱「小妖」的女網友近日投稿《臉書》不公開社團「爆廢公社」，泣訴自己好心上網買充氣娃娃安慰朋友，結果卻被詐騙集團騙錢，網頁上看起來栩栩如生的志玲姐姐充氣娃娃，實物卻像乾屍一樣、連臉都是直接拿照片印上去的，「挑了好久，李慕、楊穎、范冰冰......。」<br />\n「算了！當浮板還是蠻好用的&hellip;...。」小妖原本想退錢，賣家卻已人間蒸發，她只好跟朋友苦中作樂，替志玲姐姐穿上泳裝一起到泳池戲水，「它還會游泳喔......。」多數網友一打開照片就被逗笑了，紛紛留言調侃小妖，還有網友詢問志玲姐的「使用心得」，小妖無奈地表示，「沒試過，我朋友一直叫我放火把他燒了......。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180505/640_9e3dade35aeb10799823f15be72e1d2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180505%2F640_9e3dade35aeb10799823f15be72e1d2c.jpg&h=05ec534b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n電腦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180505/640_307d22aa38e72b25073b4ab5e2ae2ecd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180505%2F640_307d22aa38e72b25073b4ab5e2ae2ecd.jpg&h=420ecdf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b614c3c4cf8aa5dd08c8101d7c12cc51074f68","tid":653913,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:14:54.000Z","msg":"斬咗對手咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a42f37dfc9da052edf40519aee8023c97cf3971","tid":653913,"uid":5056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 擺係鬼屋嚇下人好過"},{"pid":"e13f870870ce27935c366e688abc597888265efc","tid":653913,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,